Fix: Dell Monitor/Laptop USB-C Handshake Shutdown Loop

1. Restart your laptop and tap F2 repeatedly to enter the BIOS.
2. Navigate to the Advanced Setup section and toggle it ON.
3. Navigate to the Power section.
4. Scroll down to USB Wake Support section.
5. Find Wake on Dell USB-C Dock and toggle it OFF.
6. Press F10 to save and exit.
